Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,為了米蕾優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
